0202.name: Agumon
0202.main_skill: Inflict a small amount of damage to one enemy.
0202.leader_skill: Restores a small portion of your HP.
0202.profile: A Digimon with a red waistband wrapped around its arms. It is unlike the normal Agumon. It does not distinguish between regular attacks and special moves, and it is believed that its evolution path is different.

0204.name: Renamon
0204.main_skill: Small increase in the support power of all allies.
0204.leader_skill: Small increase in the defense power of red dragon allies.
0204.profile: A Digimon of high intelligence. It can become even more intelligent through the influence of its partners or its childhood education. Its enemies are at its mercy in battles that favor speed over force.

0205.name: Kyubimon
0205.main_skill: Medium increase in the support power of all allies.
0205.leader_skill: Medium increase in the attack power of all allies.
0205.profile: A Digimon evolved from a very skilled and experienced Renamon. It is a bewitching fox. Although it is not very strong, it has a strong spirit and a variety of skills.

0208.name: Fladramon
0208.main_skill: Changes all the blue knight cards in brown recovery cards.
0208.leader_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in red dragon cards.
0208.profile: A Digimon who has armor-evolved from V-mon through the Digimental of Courage. Its combat skills are similar to a burning flame, and it hits its enemies with extremely strong knuckles.

0210.name: Grappuleomon
0210.main_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0210.leader_skill: Big increase in the attack power of all allies.
0210.profile: A martial arts Digimon who has been enlightened to some original secrets. It received its fighting data from the veteran warrior Leomon. Its digicore moves the four turbines that stand for its limbs.

0211.name: Taomon
0211.main_skill: High increase in the support power of all allies.
0211.leader_skill: Only attack cards will appear next.
0211.profile: A Digimon with a strong mind and great knowledge of Onmyodo. It can use all the skills of this art. It has many charms and dark weapons in its sleeves. It is adept at attacking its enemies from the dark.

0214.name: Ulforcevdramon
0214.main_skill: Huge increase in the attack power of red dragon allies.
0214.leader_skill: Only red dragon cards will appear next.
0214.profile: A Digimon that can freely manipulate the holy Ulforce and has the power to reconstruct digital data. It is the sacred knight predicted in the legends. It wears armor made of Blue Digizoid and has godly speed.

0215.name: Sakuyamon
0215.main_skill: Huge increase in the support power of all allies.
0215.leader_skill: Huge increase in the attack power of all allies.
0215.profile: A Digimon fulfilling the role of a miko, the agent of God's will. It has four kuda-kitsune around its waist-belt. The sound of its servants and the echo of its singing voice have the power to exorcise all evil.

0218.name: Bancholeomon
0218.main_skill: Damages all enemies while your HP drops to 1.
0218.leader_skill: Huge increase in the attack power of red dragon allies.
0218.profile: A Digimon who wins while respecting its sense of justice and holding to its beliefs. It would face even the Three Great Angels or the Royal Knights to make its sense of justice understood.

0222.name: Toyagumon
0222.main_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage to all enemies.
0222.leader_skill: Small increase in the defense of all allies.
0222.profile: A Digimon whose whole body is made of plastic blocks. It was built using Agumon as a model. However, it is very cowardly and has no courage. When it is surprised, its body breaks into pieces.

0223.name: Magnamon
0223.main_skill: Big increase in the attack power of all allies.
0223.leader_skill: Inflicts medium damage to all enemies.
0223.profile: A Digimon who armor-evolved through the Digimental of Miracles. Dressed in Chrome Digizoid armor, its power is comparable to that of an ultimate form. In times of crisis, it can escape using the power of miracles.

0225.name: Mechanorimon
0225.main_skill: Inflicts medium damage to all enemies.
0225.leader_skill: Medium increase in the defense of all allies.
0225.profile: A Powered Suit Digimon. It is run by a small Digimon inside it. A Digimon still under development, its digicore can cause overheating depending on the operating conditions.

0226.name: Giromon
0226.main_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0226.leader_skill: Only attack cards will appear next.
0226.profile: A Digimon patrolling the computer network. It fights off illegal intruders. Called the Net Keeper, it attacks any invading enemy with all its forces.

0229.name: Megadramon
0229.main_skill: Inflict most of the damage to one enemy.
0229.leader_skill: Some blue knight, brown recovery and wild cards will appear.
0229.profile: A Virus Dark Dragon Digimon. It was upgraded to be able to destroy a network by itself. It invades the computer network, destroys the host computers, and modifies them easily.

0232.name: Craniummon
0232.main_skill: Huge increase in the defense of all allies.
0232.leader_skill: Restores a large portion of your HP.
0232.profile: The most respectful Digimon of the Royal Knights. It pays respect even to its enemies during combat. It holds the legendary magic spear Claiomh Solais and the sturdy shield Avalon.

0234.name: Justimon
0234.main_skill: Inflicts most of the damage to all enemies.
0234.leader_skill: Increases the value of all cards by 1.
0234.profile: A hero of justice Digimon trailing a red muffler. It can change its arm by replacing the plug of its Extend Transmitter.

0235.name: Saintgargomon
0235.main_skill: Changes the value of all cards to 9.
0235.leader_skill: Drastically reduces the number of turns before a skill is active.
0235.profile: A huge machine Digimon equipped with high-temperature weapons on its whole body. These weapons are comparable to those carried by Metalgarurumon. It is slow but can easily repel its enemies with the power of fire.

0239.name: Kamemon
0239.main_skill: Small increase in the attack power of green nature allies.
0239.leader_skill: Inflict a small amount of damage to one enemy.
0239.profile: A Digimon equipped with a shell in the shape of a mouse and trackball on its belly. When it retreats into its shell, its defense increases significantly, but its helmet cannot fit inside.

0243.name: Sunflowmon
0243.main_skill: Inflict medium damage to one enemy.
0243.leader_skill: Medium increase in the attack power of green nature allies.
0243.profile: A Digimon that looks like a sunflower. It absorbs energy when it bathes in the sunlight. It loves basking in the sun and, on days with good weather, it flies using the leaves on its back.

0244.name: Tortamon
0244.main_skill: Medium decrease in the attack power of all enemies.
0244.leader_skill: Slightly reduces the number of turns before a skill is active.
0244.profile: A Digimon with dense armor and sharp blades. It makes a soft noise when it walks. Its moving speed is extremely slow. However, it can retract its limbs and rotate, making its speed more than 10 times greater.

0248.name: Reppamon
0248.main_skill: Inflicts medium damage to all enemies.
0248.profile: A kamaitachi-style Digimon. Its tail is a sharp blade with a will of its own. It likes to battle in the forest. It attacks together with its blade, but there are times when they don't get along very well.

0249.name: Etemon
0249.main_skill: Adds a small delay to all enemy attacks.
0249.leader_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in green nature cards.
0249.profile: A Digimon calling itself the King of Digimon. It wears a fortified monkey suit and sings its best numbers. It gets along well with Monzaemon, but it is rumored it pulls the other's strings in the shadows.

0251.name: Sagomon
0251.main_skill: High decrease in the attack power of all enemies.
0251.leader_skill: High increase in the attack power of green nature allies.
0251.profile: A Digimon with a cheerful and easy-going personality. It transforms into a dreadful Digimon if even one of the skulls at its waist disappears. It was expelled from heaven and has set out on a journey in search of its true identity.

0255.name: Leviamon
0255.main_skill: Reduces the damage received from red dragon enemies.
0255.leader_skill: Some green nature, brown recovery and wild cards will appear.
0255.profile: One of the Seven Great Demon Lords sleeping in the abyss of the Digital World. It has a huge body and is called the Devil Beast due to its very large jaw.

0258.name: Phascomon
0258.main_skill: Small increase in the defense power of purple dark allies.
0258.leader_skill: Adds a small delay to all enemy attacks.
0258.profile: A Digimon living in the Evil Forest spreading in the Dark Area. It is a dangerous Digimon, even though it doesn't look like one. It sleeps in trees all the time and sometimes attacks negligent opponents by jumping on them.

0262.name: Porcupamon
0262.main_skill: Changes all the yellow holy cards in brown recovery cards.
0262.leader_skill: Medium increase in the attack power of purple dark allies.
0262.profile: An endangered species of Digimon. It didn't live in the Dark Area originally but was driven away by other species. Its body is covered with a special razor material.

0263.name: Astamon
0263.main_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0263.leader_skill: Only purple dark cards will appear next.
0263.profile: A young noble Digimon from the Dark Area which binds together the devil-type Digimon. It has the power to surpass the ultimate form, and it attacks its enemies without mercy. Its favorite machine gun is Oro Salmon.

0265.name: Skullsatamon
0265.main_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage and restore the same amount of HP.
0265.leader_skill: Reduces the damage received from yellow holy enemies.
0265.profile: A ruined but refined Fallen Angel Digimon. Its main purposes are power and destruction. Dark power is condensed in its dark digicore.

0267.name: Marindevimon
0267.main_skill: Inflicts a large amount of damage and restore the same amount of HP.
0267.leader_skill: Medium increase in the defense power of purple dark allies.
0267.profile: A subspecies of Digimon. It is full of hatred because it lives alone in the deep sea. Its two tentacles have their own will and are free to attack on their own.

0269.name: Armagemon
0269.main_skill: Inflicts most of the damage to all enemies.
0269.leader_skill: Drastically reduces the number of turns before a skill is active.
0269.profile: A super ultimate form Digimon, formed by scattering Kuramon everywhere and then putting all the pieces together in the real world. It took over Diablomon's plans and seeks revenge against Omegamon.

0271.name: Barbamon
0271.main_skill: The yellow holy cards will not appear.
0271.profile: A Digimon living in the center of the Dark Area. It is one of Seven Great Demon Lords, the supervisors of the fallen angels. Obsessed with all the treasures in the network, it can employ any methods when it comes to materialistic issues.

0272.name: Belphemon: Ragemode
0272.main_skill: Reduces the damage received by half.
0272.leader_skill: Increases the value of all cards by 2.
0272.profile: A Digimon awakened after a long sleep. It is the incarnation of anger. Its ferocious roar is enough to disintegrate the data of weaker Digimon. It considers everything that comes into its sight to be an enemy.

0273.name: Metaletemon
0273.main_skill: Adds a big delay to all enemy attacks.
0273.leader_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in purple dark cards.
0273.profile: The 'King of Digimon' studied its weak points after each battle and coated its whole body in Chrome Digizoid. Thus, a strong and dirty warrior was born!

0274.name: Lilithmon
0274.main_skill: Inflicts a large amount of damage and restore the same amount of HP.
0274.leader_skill: Only purple dark cards will appear next.
0274.profile: The mysterious and beautiful goddess of darkness. It deceives its opponents and always brings death to those who fall into temptation. It is generous with evil and unforgiving with good.

0276.name: Kudamon
0276.main_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in yellow holy cards.
0276.leader_skill: Restores a small portion of your HP.
0276.profile: A Holy Beast Digimon with a holy shell. It always calmly analyzes the situation and leads the battle to a position favorable for it. It deposits sacred power into its earring daily, and the deposited amount can influence its evolution.

0278.name: Sanzomon
0278.leader_skill: Changes all the purple dark cards in brown recovery cards.
0278.profile: A monk Digimon who continues its journey of trials in order to find enlightenment. It holds no weapon but only sings its sutras and leads the hearts gone astray. Some Digimon aim for the pure energy stored in its digicore.

0280.name: Tyilinmon
0280.main_skill: Inflicts a large amount of damage to all enemies.
0280.leader_skill: Big increase in the attack power of all allies.
0280.profile: A Digimon who, though it has been in its Perfect form since the genesis of the Digital World, is said to hold the same power as an Ultimate form. It has a very merciful personality, but it severely punishes those who kill unjustly.

0282.name: Shakamon
0282.main_skill: Inflict most of the damage to one enemy.
0282.leader_skill: Only yellow holy and purple dark cards will appear next.
0282.profile: A Digimon originally very close to Yggdrasil. It has been protecting the eastern region for a long time and is full of affection. It sometimes gives trials to the Digital World and waits for Digimon to surmount them.
